00:09:13,502 --> 00:09:16,692
into the property, so I
put my superhero pants on

262
00:09:16,692 --> 00:09:19,391
and cape and went to sort out the problem.

263
00:09:19,391 --> 00:09:20,302
- [Son] In your dreams, Dad.

264
00:09:20,302 --> 00:09:21,135
- Yeah, all right.

265
00:09:21,135 --> 00:09:22,482
When I stepped into the warehouse,

266
00:09:22,482 --> 00:09:25,142
I was greeted by the
sight of a disheveled man

267
00:09:25,142 --> 00:09:26,722
surrounded by paperwork.

268
00:09:26,722 --> 00:09:29,932
We got talking and it turned
out he owned the property.

269
00:09:29,932 --> 00:09:31,402
After chatting with him for a while,

270
00:09:31,402 --> 00:09:34,412
I uncovered that he was in
a bit of a financial state

271
00:09:34,412 --> 00:09:37,222
and needed to sell his
warehouse as soon as possible.

272
00:09:37,222 --> 00:09:40,272
It was worth around $300,000 at the time,

273
00:09:40,272 --> 00:09:43,942
so I offered him a cool $150,000

274
00:09:43,942 --> 00:09:45,932
with the agreement that I'd pay him full

275
00:09:45,932 --> 00:09:46,782
within the week.

276
00:09:46,782 --> 00:09:48,072
He obviously said no.

277
00:09:48,072 --> 00:09:50,902
In fact, he laughed me
out of the building.

278
00:09:50,902 --> 00:09:52,542
Fast-forward a couple of days

279
00:09:52,542 --> 00:09:54,772
and he was at my door, shaking my hand,

280
00:09:54,772 --> 00:09:55,952
and we had a done deal.

281
00:09:55,952 --> 00:09:57,642
This isn't an isolated incident.

282
00:09:57,642 --> 00:10:00,762
This type of thing happens
all the time during recessions

283
00:10:00,762 --> 00:10:03,792
and you don't always
need 150,000 up-front.

284
00:10:03,792 --> 00:10:05,512
But of course it does help.

285
00:10:05,512 --> 00:10:07,312
To show you how powerful money is,

286
00:10:07,312 --> 00:10:09,642
when I bought this house,
there were six people offering

287
00:10:09,642 --> 00:10:11,172
more money than I was,

288
00:10:11,172 --> 00:10:13,672
but I got the deal because
I could offer the cash

289
00:10:13,672 --> 00:10:15,632
a lot faster than anyone else,

290
00:10:15,632 --> 00:10:18,192
and that's enabled me to
nearly finish the north wing.

291
00:10:18,192 --> 00:10:21,162
A recession does two
very important things.

292
00:10:21,162 --> 00:10:23,102
First, it puts pressure on the sellers,

293
00:10:23,102 --> 00:10:24,592
as they might have lost their jobs

294
00:10:24,592 --> 00:10:26,482
or had their incomes slashed.

295
00:10:26,482 --> 00:10:28,612
This means that they
could be finding it harder

296
00:10:28,612 --> 00:10:30,052
to meet their mortgage payments

297
00:10:30,052 --> 00:10:31,582
and are being forced to sell.

298
00:10:31,582 --> 00:10:33,842
Second, it cuts down the amount of buyers,

299
00:10:33,842 --> 00:10:36,282
as most people didn't
prepare like you did,

300
00:10:36,282 --> 00:10:37,802
and therefore have no money

301
00:10:37,802 --> 00:10:39,242
and a weak credit score.

302
00:10:39,242 --> 00:10:41,732
These two things together flip the market

303
00:10:41,732 --> 00:10:44,242
from a seller's market
to a buyer's market.

304
00:10:44,242 --> 00:10:46,202
If you could fine a property off-market,

305
00:10:46,202 --> 00:10:48,172
like I did, then that's even better,

306
00:10:48,172 --> 00:10:50,192
as you're able to cut out the agent fees

307
00:10:50,192 --> 00:10:51,822
and also have less competition.

308
00:10:51,822 --> 00:10:53,832
Even if you don't have
money during these times,

309
00:10:53,832 --> 00:10:55,232
you can still make a profit

310
00:10:55,232 --> 00:10:57,672
from deal-sourcing, and
even flipping houses

311
00:10:57,672 --> 00:10:58,852
with an investor.

312
00:10:58,852 --> 00:11:01,352
The absolute best time to buy is when

313
00:11:01,352 --> 00:11:02,932
everything is discounted

314
00:11:02,932 --> 00:11:05,842
so you could build equity during a boom,

315
00:11:05,842 --> 00:11:08,592
smash that wall down,
and enjoy the profits.

316
00:11:08,592 --> 00:11:10,442
So I'm gonna leave the
next video right up there,

317
00:11:10,442 --> 00:11:11,852
but don't click on it just yet.

318
00:11:11,852 --> 00:11:14,522
Make sure to subscribe if
you wanna grow your wealth.

